	</font>

78
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,720
<font color=#00ff00>
	Kümmel.
	</font>

79
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,000
<font color=#00ff00>
	Schwarzer Pfeffer.
	</font>

80
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:42,160
<font color=#00ff00>
	Mindestens vier Stunden kochen
	</font>
<font color=#00ff00>
