	</font>
<font color=#00ff00>
	Küchenpapier lassen.
	</font>

97
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,760
<font color=#00ff00>
	Offenstehen lassen,
	</font>

98
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,720
<font color=#00ff00>
